  "detailed_description": "Imprisoned deep in ZYNET, an unexpected ally will grant you the power to take control of your destiny.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1246170/extras/2fbaa397ddd09a10749dab1bc46b7c8a.poster.avif?t=1632146230\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1246170/extras/2fbaa397ddd09a10749dab1bc46b7c8a.webm?t=1632146230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1246170/extras/2fbaa397ddd09a10749dab1bc46b7c8a.mp4?t=1632146230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>How you will escape ZYNET:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>To move and fight you will <strong>toss</strong> your discs with quick reflexes and deadly accuracy<br></li><li>To build your score multiplier and maximize your destruction you will maneuver your discs with perfectly timed <strong>swipes</strong><br></li><li>To keep your momentum going you will <strong>dodge</strong> and <strong>punch</strong> away everything in your path<br></li><li>To unlock your true potential you will gain the ability to <strong>take control</strong> of anything you come across and will bash or launch it into oblivion<br></li><li>To earn the power needed to traverse through ZYNET you will destroy anything and everything with ludicrous <strong>speed</strong></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1246170/extras/4cd7d869c207a946fa578518d6e0e02c.poster.avif?t=1632146230\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1246170/extras/4cd7d869c207a946fa578518d6e0e02c.webm?t=1632146230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1246170/extras/4cd7d869c207a946fa578518d6e0e02c.mp4?t=1632146230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Early Access currently has 14 unique levels taking roughly between 4 to 6 hours for a single play through.  Both the star power system and global leaderboards will reward you for many more hours of play.",
